+## Qwen Added Memories
+- Refactored the Armeria codebase to improve maintainability and consistency by updating Gradle build files to use modern dependency management, improving documentation and conventions in README and CONTRIBUTING.md, adding utility functions in a new Util class, and refactoring settings.gradle to have clean project configurations.
